{"tid":1278046,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"自首即係認罪 公民抗命唔代表要認罪","createTime":"2019-07-02T10:48:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T11:07:20.000Z","uid":40980,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f471dcdb74973dc8ce2bc0497a167c0d82c159b1","tid":1278046,"uid":40980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:48:30.000Z","msg":"用公民抗命黎抗辯換取減輕罪責，主要解釋到自己 (1)「行事時應有合理的節制，不能造成過份的破壞或對公眾造成太大的不便」；同埋 (2) 「接受法律施加的懲罰」。<br />\n<br />\n尋晚發夢攪成咁，要證明第一點其實已經唔太容易。同時發夢時又戴晒口罩，要證明第二點就更難，因為口罩會俾人話係用黎隱蔽身份，咁就好難兜到自己係接受法律施加的懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n所以叫人自首果D 你諗清楚係咪夠理據話自己係公民抗命，唔好鳩講叫兄弟去送頭<br />\n<br />\n雖然係戴妖寫，但值得一睇:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.role.hku.hk/articles/post/59c4c2d50feacb3f07fca314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.role.hku.hk%2Farticles%2Fpost%2F59c4c2d50feacb3f07fca314&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPj1D2OVAb2WcgpQnG2a6kfc%3D&h=56349df8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.role.hku.hk/articles/post/59c4c2d50feacb3f07fca314</a><br />\n<br />\n利申：非law底，有錯請屌"},{"pid":"3e27f13b1b97d839b3e4b3e7042d3932348e3e21","tid":1278046,"uid":40980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:53:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8bcb98ac5c86658467e9309f60b66f04d4c5cc73","tid":1278046,"uid":40980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:54:09.000Z","msg":"勁快沉底"},{"pid":"4850889d3ba77aba6c75103c79eaad167eb5bb09","tid":1278046,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463aaa0b201c321c3425e73557c9e7578e7fdbfd","tid":1278046,"uid":40980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:56:25.000Z","msg":"有無法律撚可以入黎講下，我都驚自己講錯"},{"pid":"d18fad406d0dcabc2beacc2237d6c8ab75a35351","tid":1278046,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22